text: Everybody  Please Be Safe On the Internet Usually Reddit is an amazing place to meet new people  but please please please be careful  I just had someone try to get me to send him some very inappropriate things on this platform and I just finished reporting him to the police   Everybody  they prey on us because they know we are insecure and vulnerable  If someone starts asking or talking about inappropriate things and you are a minor  collect as much information as you can  don t send them anything  and report them to the police  They may be preying on other kids  Don t let them get away with it   If you want to report them without your parents finding out  google WeTip  It s a way to make an anonymous police report  You never give them your name  and they will not contact you further  Also  if you report someone and they end up being arrested  apparently you get a reward   Please  if you see something  do something  I never want to relive that experience and I don t want anyone to ever fall victim to anyone like that again   Please be careful
summary: Reddit is an amazing place to meet new people but please be careful on the Internet. Someone tried to get me to send him inappropriate things on Reddit and I just finished reporting him to the police. They prey on us because they know we are insecure and vulnerable.
